<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Confeitaria - Home</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #fff0f6;
      margin: 0;
      color: #700a32;
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; }

    /* ================= BANNER ================= */
    .banner {
      background:#ffc0cb;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      border-radius: 35px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(233,158,185,0.3);
      margin: 50px auto;
      max-width: 1000px;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
    }

    .banner h1 {
      font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      color: #d9155c;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .banner p {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #c2185b;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .btn-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d9155c, #f48bae);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 35px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 35px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(233,158,185,0.3);
    }

    .btn-banner:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f48bae, #ffe6f0);
      color: #700a32;
    }

    /* ================= SEÇÃO DE CARDS ================= */
    .cards-section {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 60px auto;
      max-width: 1000px;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff0f6;
      border-radius: 35px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(233,158,185,0.3);
      padding: 30px 25px;
      flex: 1 1 420px;
      min-height: 350px;
      transition: 0.3s;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(233,158,185,0.4);
    }

    .card h2 {
      color: #d9155c;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .card p {
      color: #700a32;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .card img {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(233,158,185,0.3);
    }

    /* ================= CONTATO ================= */
    .contato-info {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #700a32;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contato-info p {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .contato-info i {
      color: #d9155c;
    }

    /* ================= ANIMAÇÕES ================= */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ================= RESPONSIVIDADE ================= */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .banner h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      .banner p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .cards-section {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 25px;
      }
      .card {
        min-height: auto;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <!-- BANNER -->
    <section class="banner">
      <h1>Bem-vindo à nossa Confeitaria</h1>
      <p>Delícias preparadas com carinho e um toque de amor!</p>
      <a href="/loja/categorias" class="btn-banner">Faça seu pedido</a>
    </section>

    <!-- SOBRE + CONTATO -->
    <section class="cards-section">
      <!-- Card SOBRE -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Conheça nossa história</h2>
        <img src="/imagens/foto-dona.png" alt="Dona da Confeitaria">
        <p>
          Nossa confeitaria nasceu do sonho da <strong>Luciane</strong>, apaixonada por criar doces e bolos que encantam. 
          Cada receita é feita com ingredientes selecionados, muito carinho e dedicação. 
          Aqui, cada cliente é parte da nossa história doce!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card CONTATO -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Fale conosco</h2>
        <div class="contato-info">
          <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Rua Serafim Manoel de Souza, 457 – Araranguá</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> (48) 99817-3326</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> adm.ludoces@gmail.com</p>
          <p><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i> @_ludoces_</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
